âš ï¸ 8. Safety / Design Tips

Never force the servo by hand â†’ gears break

Keep ultrasonic sensors clean

Do not put heavy trash directly on top sensor

Keep wires away from servo arm

Use external 5V supply if servo draws too much power

Add rubber feet to reduce vibration

ğŸ§¼ 9. Maintenance Tips

Clean ultrasonic sensor holes weekly

Recalibrate BIN_HEIGHT_CM if bin layout changes

Tighten servo mounts monthly

Check for loose jumper wires

Keep LCD covered from dust
